<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Conectar nova conta — MeliSync for GDA</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --yellow: #FFE600;
      --dark: #1A1A18;
      --bg: #FFFDF7;
      --card-bg: #ffffff;
      --border: #E8E6DE;
      --text-muted: #888888;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--yellow);
      padding: 0 2rem;
      height: 60px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .topbar-left {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .topbar-logo {
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .topbar-logo-text {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .topbar-by {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--dark);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .main {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .page-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .steps {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      min-width: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--yellow);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .step-content strong {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .step-content span {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .cta {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--yellow);
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }

    .btn-dark:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    .btn-yellow {
      background: var(--yellow);
      color: var(--dark);
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }

    .btn-yellow:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover { background: #f5f3eb; }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #bbb;
    }
  </style>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon-180x180.png" />
</head>
<body>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-left">
      <div class="topbar-logo">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="display:block;flex-shrink:0;">
          <rect width="200" height="200" rx="44" fill="#1A1A18"/>
          <path d="M100 36 A64 64 0 1 1 36 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFE600" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <polygon points="31,78 31,116 62,97" fill="#FFE600"/>
          <text x="100" y="122" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Sora', Georgia, sans-serif" font-size="66" font-weight="700" fill="#FFE600">M</text>
        </svg>
        <div class="topbar-logo-text">
          <span>MeliSync</span><span>for GDA</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="topbar-by">by MS1 Softwares</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="main">

    <p class="page-title">Conectar nova conta</p>
    <p class="page-sub">Para trocar de conta no Mercado Livre, siga os passos abaixo:</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <strong>Abra o Mercado Livre</strong>
          <span>Acesse mercadolivre.com.br em uma nova aba</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <strong>Faça logout</strong>
          <span>Clique no seu nome → Sair da conta</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <strong>Volte aqui e continue</strong>
          <span>Clique no botão abaixo para prosseguir com a nova conta</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <a href="https://www.mercadolivre.com.br" target="_blank" class="btn-dark">Abrir Mercado Livre</a>
      <a href="/auth/mercadolivre?skip=1" class="btn-yellow">Já fiz logout — continuar →</a>
      <a href="/" class="btn-ghost">Cancelar</a>
    </div>

  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    MeliSync for GDA · MS1 Softwares
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
